name: Sam Tandy
title: For strong bones, if you need more calcium in your diet...
review: I have 100g every morning, added to my cereal to raise my calcium levels, and also use it on pies and desserts instead of ice cream. It's thick and rich, and only 72 calories for 100g (there are 500 g in a 17.6 oz container). It's ruined my taste for other yogurts.

review: Best tasting, reduced fat, greek-style yoghurt. Delicious on toast, with either jam, or with seeds sprinkled on top.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on June 23, 2021
name: christina
title: The best yogurt
review: Fage yogurts are the best real yogurts in the market. This is a Greek family business that started locally and has expanded all over the globe.No wonder why. The flavor, the texture and the softness are characteristics of delicious authentice Greek yogurt.100% recommended.

review_data: Reviewed in the United States on May 22, 2021
name: Stacey
title: Face Yogurts are the bomb
review: I've been satisfied with every Fage yogurt I've purchased -- from 0 fat to 5%. They are all good tasting and a nice texture. I mix it with fruit and use it like sour cream on tacos and baked potatoes. Solid quality.
